      "description": "Solid classic driver with lots of vintage charm and an inviting price point for someone looking to get into the hobby. This one presents well enough to enjoy around town and at local meets, with the kind of honest character that makes owning an older car fun. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a respectable fair-condition example that offers style, presence, and plenty of enjoyment for the money.",
