    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "An exceptional mint-condition example that presents beautifully throughout and should satisfy a buyer looking for one of the nicest cars on the market. The paint, body, brightwork, and interior all show to a very high standard, with the kind of fit, finish, and overall presentation you expect from a carefully kept, top-level car. It appears extremely well cared for, with excellent cosmetics and the sort of clean, sorted impression that suggests very little if anything will be needed beyond routine enjoyment and upkeep. This is not just a usable driver or a tidy weekend car\u2014it is a standout example for someone who wants a car that shows exceptionally well and feels special to own.",
